ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is a great class! You'll be reading the "modern" thinkers from Spinoza through Karelitz. Professor Stern encourages debate and engagement with the material.
I highly recommend this course. The subject matter is interesting and fundamental to anybody interested in Judaic studies and political philosophy. Theprofessor is engaging and knowledgeable.
A great survey of major Jewish thinkers, mostly from Western Europe. I would absolutely recommend it if you are interested in the subject.
